{"pr_pilot":{"received_at":"2026-04-28T06:09:21Z","event_type":"pull_request","action":"opened","category":"actionable"},"payload":{"action":"opened","number":2728,"pull_request":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/strawgate/fastforward/pulls/2728","id":3594036681,"node_id":"PR_kwDORzg8fM7WOKXJ","html_url":"https://github.com/strawgate/fastforward/pull/2728","diff_url":"https://github.com/strawgate/fastforward/pull/2728.diff","patch_url":"https://github.com/strawgate/fastforward/pull/2728.patch","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/strawgate/fastforward/issues/2728","number":2728,"state":"open","locked":false,"title":"fix/runtime: PermanentError uses Reject; add design notes on known issues","user":{"login":"strawgate","id":6384545,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjYzODQ1NDU=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/6384545?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/strawgate","html_url":"https://github.com/strawgate","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/strawgate/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/strawgate/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/strawgate/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/strawgate/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/strawgate/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/strawgate/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/strawgate/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/strawgate/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/strawgate/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"body":"## Summary\n\n- **Fix**: `PermanentError` (submit.rs:102) now uses `TicketDisposition::Reject` instead of `Ack`. The semantic intent is that a permanently rejected batch should reject its checkpoint ticket, not acknowledge it.\n- **Docs**: Added `NOTE:` comments at 4 sites documenting known behavioral issues that have caused confusion during bug sweeps.\n\n## Changes\n\n| File | Change |\n|------|--------|\n| `submit.rs:102` | `PermanentError`: `Ack` \u2192 `Reject` |\n| `submit.rs:154` | NOTE: `inflight_batches` counter not decremented on early-return paths |\n| `run.rs:193` | NOTE: terminal path abandons batches already in channel |\n| `run.rs:463` | NOTE: `held_tickets` grows unboundedly with transient failures |\n| `reader.rs:351` | NOTE: `evicted_offsets` grows unboundedly with high-frequency log rotation |\n\n## Testing\n\n- `cargo test -p ffwd-runtime` \u2014 249 tests pass\n- `cargo check -p ffwd-runtime -p ffwd-io` \u2014 clean\n\n## Notes\n\nThe 4 known issues documented with `NOTE:` comments are tracked separately as issue #2475 sub-items.","created_at":"2026-04-28T06:09:17Z","updated_at":"2026-04-28T06:09:18Z","closed_at":null,"merged_at":null,"merge_commit_sha":null,"assignees":[],"requested_reviewers":[{"login":"Copilot","id":175728472,"node_id":"BOT_kgDOCnlnWA","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/in/946600?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/Copilot","html_url":"https://github.com/apps/copilot-pull-request-reviewer","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Copilot/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Copilot/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Copilot/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Copilot/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Copilot/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Copilot/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Copilot/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Copilot/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/Copilot/received_events","type":"Bot","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false}],"requested_teams":[],"labels":[],"milestone":null,"draft":false,"commits_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/strawgate/fastforward/pulls/2728/commits","revi